# Layer 3 hash blocklist (csam_hashes.txt) — NOT shipped.
#
# One ed2k/MD4 hash per line as 32 hex characters. An optional ';' inline
# comment may follow the hash. Lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
#   0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef ; optional note
#
# Obtain hashes ONLY from authoritative sources (NCMEC, IWF hash list,
# Project Arachnid / Canadian Centre for Child Protection). These lists are
# typically licensed and MUST NOT be redistributed publicly — keep this file
# private and out of version control.
#
# Absent/empty -> Layer 3 inactive (allowed only when server.public = false;
# a public server requires a non-empty blocklist, enforced in main.rs).
#
# (Intentionally empty — populate locally; template only.)
